Dosage was calculated using the formula Dosage = dose prescribed/weight
Penicilin Under dose - a prescription of less than 40,000iu/kg
Penicillin Overdose - a prescription >60,000 iu/kg
Penicillin Correct dose - a prescription >=40000 & <=60000 iu/kg

#Gentamicin Underdose - a prescription <2.4mg/kg for weight below 2kg or <4mg/kg for weight >=2kg. #Gentamicin Overdose - a prescription >3.6mg/kg for weight below 2kg or <6mg/kg for weight >=2kg.
